  <brief_title>Postspinal Hypotension and Cardiac Performance in the Elderly</brief_title>
  <official_title>Is Postspinal Hypotension a Sign of Impaired Cardiac Performance in the Elderly? An Observational Mechanistic Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
